Usage: ecoSwapSpareCell [-help] <inst> <inst> [-keepScan] [-noScanTrace]
                        [-preservePin <string>] [-suffix <string>]

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
<inst>                    # Name of instance ((inst), required)
<inst>                    # Name of spareCell instance ((inst), required)
-keepScan                 # (bool, optional)
-noScanTrace              # disable scan trace (bool, optional)
-preservePin <string>     # (string, optional)
-suffix <string>          # (string, optional)